{
  "id": "69c875490561d54e54f6c5c5",
  "title": "飲食店に求めること",
  "created": 1774744906,
  "updated": 1774750895,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c875490561d54e54f6c5c5",
      "text": "飲食店に求めること",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744906,
      "updated": 1774744910
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875490000000000d33981",
      "text": "from [2026/03/28]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744906,
      "updated": 1774744906
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875490000000000d33982",
      "text": "飲食店に求めること",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744906,
      "updated": 1774744915
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875550000000000d3398b",
      "text": "[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744918,
      "updated": 1774744918
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875490000000000d33983",
      "text": " 5歳の娘が好きな飲食店は食事が美味しいとかではない",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744906,
      "updated": 1774744906
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875490000000000d33984",
      "text": "  なにかもらえる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744906,
      "updated": 1774744906
    },
    {
      "id": "69c887f800000000009eb900",
      "text": "  \t[魚べい]でルーレット回すとコイン貰えたの、結構楽しかったな[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774749688,
      "updated": 1774749775
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8883600000000009eb901",
      "text": "  \tコイン貰うと[ガチャポン]回せた",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774749751,
      "updated": 1774749765
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875490000000000d33985",
      "text": "  店員さんやお客さんが子供とコミュニケーションしてくれる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744906,
      "updated": 1774744906
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875490000000000d33986",
      "text": "  我々の思う飲食店の感覚ではなく、テーマパークの感覚に近いのかな[Hiro Aki.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744906,
      "updated": 1774744906
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875490000000000d33987",
      "text": "  大人も食事に求めるものは様々あり、体験を買う的なものもあるように思う",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744906,
      "updated": 1774744906
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875490000000000d33988",
      "text": "  \tチェーン店でない店に入るとかはこっちの要素も大きいかも",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744906,
      "updated": 1774744906
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875490000000000d33989",
      "text": "  \t\tカフェとか特にコーヒーの味より店の雰囲気みたいなものの方が重視される（自分の場合）",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744906,
      "updated": 1774744906
    },
    {
      "id": "69c875490000000000d3398a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1774744906,
      "updated": 1774744906
    },
    {
      "id": "69c88a9f00000000009eb90d",
      "text": "「飲食店」をもう少し細分化する[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750368,
      "updated": 1774750381
    },
    {
      "id": "69c88aa100000000009eb90f",
      "text": "\t個人店に求めること",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750370,
      "updated": 1774750388
    },
    {
      "id": "69c88c4900000000009eb913",
      "text": "\t\t体験",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750794,
      "updated": 1774750797
    },
    {
      "id": "69c88c5b00000000009eb915",
      "text": "\t\t\t知らない料理を楽しむ体験",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750811,
      "updated": 1774750816
    },
    {
      "id": "69c88c4f00000000009eb914",
      "text": "\t\t料理の美味しさ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750800,
      "updated": 1774750803
    },
    {
      "id": "69c88c6000000000009eb916",
      "text": "\t\t提供速度はそんなに期待してない[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750817,
      "updated": 1774750824
    },
    {
      "id": "69c88c6b00000000009eb917",
      "text": "\t\t\tなので時間に余裕がある時に行く感じ",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750827,
      "updated": 1774750838
    },
    {
      "id": "69c88ab300000000009eb910",
      "text": "\tチェーン店（資本系）に求めること",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750388,
      "updated": 1774750397
    },
    {
      "id": "69c88c7900000000009eb918",
      "text": "\t\t味の安定性",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750842,
      "updated": 1774750846
    },
    {
      "id": "69c88c7e00000000009eb919",
      "text": "\t\t提供速度",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750847,
      "updated": 1774750849
    },
    {
      "id": "69c88c8100000000009eb91a",
      "text": "\t\tただ確実にお腹を満たしたい時や食事をしたい時に行く感じ[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750849,
      "updated": 1774750873
    },
    {
      "id": "69c88aa100000000009eb90e",
      "text": "\t家系ラーメン店や二郎系ラーメン店に求めること",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750370,
      "updated": 1774750418
    },
    {
      "id": "69c88c9a00000000009eb91b",
      "text": "\t\t量",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750874,
      "updated": 1774750882
    },
    {
      "id": "69c88ca200000000009eb91c",
      "text": "\t\t[エネルギー不足]の時に行く感じ[Mijikko.icon]",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750882,
      "updated": 1774750895
    },
    {
      "id": "69c88ac200000000009eb912",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "60fb0a79f3364000237838e3",
      "created": 1774750403,
      "updated": 1774750403
    }
  ]
}